description:
The time has come for Sonic Underground Warriors to take a stand against tyranny. Pick up your sword and choose a side! The right one(Sonic Underground) or the fucking stupid one(the other one).

Want to help support the Sonic Underground in this war? Then why not join my Patreon for some extra goods! - https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
